Created a version that runs locally on a single default docker node instead of swarm cluster. This is primarily for development and testing. Shell scripts for it are:
run_local.sh - which starts all microservices and the dependency services like mongo DB and Kafka MQ
stop_local.sh - stops all services if started
shell_local.sh - used to get on to the container's shell for debugging
docker logs <service-name> - can be used to check the logs spewed to stdout of each service. This is useful while debugging.
